org.gitlab.api

Class GitlabBranch.ProjectQuery

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gitlab.api.GitlabBranch.ProjectQuery
  • Enclosing class:
    GitlabBranch

    public static class GitlabBranch.ProjectQuery
extends java.lang.Object
    This extends GitlabQuery and supports query for GitlabBranches within a GitlabProject with searching scope and range. Build this query with setters and call query() to execute query.

    Gitlab Web API: https://docs.gitlab.com/ee/api/branches.html#list-repository-branches

    GET /projects/:id/repository/branches
